## Common Development Tasks

### PlatformIO Commands
```bash
# Build firmware
pio run

# Upload to target
pio run --target upload

# Serial monitor
pio device monitor

# Clean build
pio run --target clean

# Run tests
pio test
```

### Programming Notes
{{PROGRAMMING_NOTES}}
